gent，description写清楚数据路径和图表类型。\\\\n</think>\\\\n\\\\n\', \'index\': 0, \'id\': \'chatcmpl-tool-966412af51d4fb3a\', \'name\': \'task\', \'args\': \'{\\"description\\": \\"使用 ECharts 生成折线图，X轴为月份（1-12），Y轴为订单总金额，每个城市（北京、上海、深圳）作为独立折线。数据源路径：/data/workspace/artifacts/data_analysis_da000a8d-e8ef-437d-8608-ee2a43f4799c/dataframes/result.parquet\\", \\"subagent_type\\": \\"visualizer_agent\\"}\'}], \'additional_kwargs\': {}, \'response_metadata\': {\'finish_reason\': \'tool_calls\', \'model_name\': \'/data/models/Qwen3-Omni-30B-A3B-Thinking-AWQ-4bit\', \'model_provider\': \'openai\', \'output_version\': \'v1\'}, \'type\': \'ai\', \'name\': None, \'id\': \'lc_run--019bf63d-b47d-7f62-bcaf-dcc63a61ab12\', \'tool_calls\': "}'}
