agent-worker  | [AuditWorker Debug] Batch count: 10. First item type: <class 'dict'>. Content: {'event_id': 'eba37928-8f0a-49f4-95f5-cec5f2a327a7', 'schema_version': '1', 'event_type': 'llm_output_received', 'event_time': '1769364531.579759', 'run_id': 'e91d4e21-9cc1-4125-bcec-25229166d2c0', 'session_id': 'ac4b20e1-6ede-49a6-aa0e-66b363008776', 'thread_id': 'e2d31d76-5154-484e-b876-13eaf7dcf22a', 'span_id': '019bf658-05fa-70e1-872c-ebe3f6ae9223', 'parent_span_id': '', 'component': 'llm', 'actor_type': 'agent', 'actor_id': 'worker', 'payload_json': '{"generations_digest": "[\'<think>\\\\n首先，用户需求是执行 SQL 查询：SELECT city, DATE_FORMAT(order_date, \\\\\'%Y-%m\\\\\') AS month, SUM(order_amount) AS total_amount FROM orders GROUP BY city, month\\\\n\\\\n但待审核的 SQL 是：\\\\n```sql\\\\nSELECT \\\\n    mc.name AS city,\\\\n    DATE_FORMAT(mo.created_at, \\\\\'%Y-%m\\\\\') AS month,\\\\n    SUM(mo.amount) AS total_amount\\\\nFROM \\\\n    m_orders mo\\\\nJOIN \\\\n    m_customers mcust ON mo.customer_id = mcust.id\\\\nJOIN \\\\n    m_cities mc ON mcust.city_id = mc.id\\\\nGROUP BY \\\\n    mc.name, \\\\n    DATE_FORMAT(mo.created_at, \\\\\'%Y-%m\\\\\');\\\\n```\\\\n\\\\n我需要审核这个 SQL 是否有逻辑错误，并判断是否符合用户需求。\\\\n\\\\n审核清单：\\\\n1. **JOIN 关联正确性**：\\\\n   - 表：m_orders (mo), m_customers (mcust), m_cities (mc)\\\\n   - 关联：mo.customer_id = mcust.id 和 mcust.city_id = mc.id\\\\n   - 根据 Schema：\\\\n     - m_orders: id, customer_id, created_at, amount, status\\\\n     - m_customers: id, name, city_id\\\\n     - m_cities: id, name\\\\n   - 所以，customer_id 是 m_orders 的外键指向 m_customers.id，city_id 是 m_customers 的外键指向 m_cities.id。关联正确，没有笛卡尔积，因为每个 join 都基于外键。\\\\n\\\\n2. **语义正确性**：\\\\n   - 用户需求：查询城市、月份、总订单金额。\\\\n   - 待审核 SQL：SELECT mc.name AS city, DATE_FORMAT(mo.created_at, \\\\\'%Y-%m\\\\\') AS month, SUM(mo.amount) AS total_amount\\\\n     - mc.name 是城市名称，来自 m_cities 表，正确。\\\\n     - DATE_FORMAT(mo.created_at, \\\\\'%Y-%m\\\\\') 是月份，但用户需求中是 order_date，这里用 created_at。在 m_orders 表中，有 created_at 字段，但用户需求说 order_date。Schema 中 m_orders 有 created_at，但用户需求是 order_date。可能 created_at 就是订单创建时间，相当于 order_date。\\\\n     - 用户需求：SELECT city, DATE_FORMAT(order_date, \\\\\'%Y-%m\\\\\') AS month, SUM(order_amount) AS total_amount\\\\n     - 待审核 SQL：用 mo.created_at 代替 order_date。在 Schema 中，m_orders 有 created_at，但用户需求说 order_date。可能 order_date 就是 created_at，或者可能有歧义。\\\\n     - 检查 Schema：m_orders (id, customer_id, created_at, amount, status) — 没有 order_date 字段。用户需求中提到了 order_date，但 Schema 中是 created_at。可能 created_at 就是订单日期。\\\\n     - 所以，这里应该没问题，created_at 代表订单日期。\\\\n     - SUM(mo.amount)：用户需求是 order_amount，这里用 amount，可能一致。\\\\n     - SELECT 的字段：city 来自 mc.name，正确；month 来自 DATE_FORMAT(mo.created_at)，正确；total_amount 来自 SUM(mo.amount)，正确。\\\\n     - 别名：city, mont", "token_usage": null}'}
