ed_at here.\\\\n\\\\nSo the correct column is created_at. So DATE_FORMAT(created_at, \\\\\'%Y-%m\\\\\') as the month.\\\\n\\\\nThen, sum the amount for each city and month.\\\\n\\\\nSo the query should select city name from m_cities, the formatted date, and sum(amount).\\\\n\\\\nBut need to group by city name and the formatted month.\\\\n\\\\nWait, the user says \\"按城市和月份统计订单总金额\\", so group by city (name) and month (formatted as \\\\\'YYYY-MM\\\\\').\\\\n\\\\nBut in SQL, when grouping by a formatted string, we need to group by the same expression as in select. So group by DATE_FORMAT(created_at, \\\\\'%Y-%m\\\\\') and city name.\\\\n\\\\nBut since we\\\\\'re joining to m_cities, the city name comes from m_cities.name.\\\\n\\\\nSo steps:\\\\n\\\\", "token_usage": null}'}
