后可视化，最后报告。\\\\n</think>\\\\n\\\\n\', \'index\': 0, \'id\': \'chatcmpl-tool-a0e26b2e2c4a9559\', \'name\': \'task\', \'args\': \'{\\"description\\": \\"处理结果数据：将month列转换为datetime类型，按城市分组后按月份排序，生成长格式DataFrame以便可视化\\", \\"subagent_type\\": \\"python_agent\\"}\'}], \'additional_kwargs\': {}, \'response_metadata\': {\'finish_reason\': \'tool_calls\', \'model_name\': \'/data/models/Qwen3-Omni-30B-A3B-Thinking-AWQ-4bit\', \'model_provider\': \'openai\', \'output_version\': \'v1\'}, \'type\': \'ai\', \'name\': None, \'id\': \'lc_run--019bf66a-979c-7830-bf15-12b15e2976dd\', \'tool_calls\': [{\'name\': \'task\', \'args\': {\'description\': \'处理结果数据：将month列转换为datetime类型，按城市分组后按月份排序，生成长格式DataFrame以便可视化\', \'subagent_type\': \'python_agent\'}, \'id\'"}'}
