agent-worker  | [AuditWorker Debug] Batch count: 10. First item type: <class 'dict'>. Content: {'event_id': '8aecfa33-4bc1-4aa5-9936-00a444013fb7', 'schema_version': '1', 'event_type': 'llm_called', 'event_time': '1769428969.7530303', 'run_id': 'c5ca0649-496e-4ce9-aa7c-9ef88fd1d919', 'session_id': '4d1ad319-399b-498c-87bf-cb531ae6cb03', 'thread_id': '2cbe42b3-839c-4b4b-8de1-c32e37a21c82', 'span_id': '019bfa2f-6918-76d1-8376-9d017131cb52', 'parent_span_id': '019bfa2f-690b-7111-bea6-3a224f727d34', 'component': 'llm', 'actor_type': 'agent', 'actor_id': 'worker', 'payload_json': '{"model": "/data/models/Qwen3-Omni-30B-A3B-Thinking-AWQ-4bit", "prompts_digest": "[\'Human: 你是 SQL 审核专家。审核以下 SQL 是否存在逻辑错误，并判断是否符合用户需求。\\\\n\\\\n**用户需求**：\\\\n执行SQL查询，按城市和月份聚合订单总金额。参数：数据库名=orders_db，查询需求=\\\\\'SELECT city, DATE_FORMAT(order_date, \\\\\'%Y-%m\\\\\') AS month, SUM(order_amount) AS total_amount FROM orders GROUP BY city, month ORDER BY month\\\\\'\\\\n\\\\n**数据库 Schema**：\\\\n- agent_checkpoints: (id, thread_id, checkpoint_ns, checkpoint, version, created_at, updated_at)\\\\n- events: (id, ts, level, type, pipeline, node, stream_id, msg, extra)\\\\n- graphs: (id, name, requires, file_path, created_at, updated_at)\\\\n- logs: (id, ts, level, pipeline, node, stream_id, message, extra)\\\\n- m_cities: (id, name)\\\\n- m_customers: (id, name, city_id)\\\\n- m_orders: (id, customer_id, created_at, amount, status)\\\\n- models: (id, task, family, variant, path, conf, iou, created_at, updated_at)\\\\n- pipelines: (name, graph_id, default_model_id, encoder_cfg, created_at, updated_at)\\\\n- sessions: (id, stream_id, pipeline, model_id, status, error_msg, started_at, stopped_at)\\\\n- sources: (id, uri, status, caps, fps, created_at, updated_at)\\\\n- train_jobs: (id, status, phase, cfg, mlflow_run_id, registered_model, registered_version, metrics, artifacts, error)\\\\n\\\\n**待审核 SQL**：\\\\n```sql\\\\nSELECT\\\\n    m_cities.name AS city,\\\\n    DATE_FORMAT(m_orders.created_at, \\\\\'%Y-%m\\\\\') AS month,\\\\n    SUM(m_orders.amount) AS total_amount\\\\nFROM\\\\n    m_orders\\\\nJOIN\\\\n    m_customers ON m_orders.customer_id = m_customers.id\\\\nJOIN\\\\n    m_cities ON m_customers.city_id = m_cities.id\\\\nGROUP BY\\\\n    city, month\\\\nORDER BY\\\\n    month;\\\\n```\\\\n\\\\n**审核清单**：\\\\n1. **JOIN 关联正确性**：JOIN 条件是否通过正确的外键关联？是否会产生笛卡尔积？\\\\n2. **语义正确性**（最重要）：\\\\n   - SELECT 的字段必须来自语义正确的表。根据 Schema 中的外键关系判断。\\\\n   - 如果用户要查某个维度的统计（如城市、类别），SELECT 的名称字段必须来自该维度的最终表，不能来自中间关联表。\\\\n   - SELECT 的别名应该反映其真实含义。\\\\n3. **聚合粒度**：\\\\n   - 如果用户需要\\"饼图/占比/分布\\"，SQL 应该只按一个维度聚合（如只 GROUP BY city_name）。\\\\n   - 如果用户需要\\"趋势图/时序图\\"，SQL 应该包含时间维度聚合。\\\\n4. **GROUP BY (宽松模式)**：只要 SELECT 中的非聚合列在 GROUP BY 中出现且逻辑正确，就通过。\\\\n\\\\n**回复格式**（必须是有效 JSON）：\\\\n{\\"approved\\": true, \\"issues\\": [], \\"suggestion\\": \\"\\"}\\\\n或\\\\n{\\"approved\\": false, \\"iss"}'}
