agent-worker  | [AuditWorker Debug] Batch count: 10. First item type: <class 'dict'>. Content: {'event_id': '218de798-49c2-4f20-8315-a73878bc884f', 'schema_version': '1', 'event_type': 'llm_called', 'event_time': '1769437166.8885689', 'run_id': 'ac754322-dd09-40f2-8814-cc6e2d861d62', 'session_id': 'b0a41bf5-635c-4d68-bce8-1789e9e5b99a', 'thread_id': '4340f8ce-dca6-4557-9565-912623e717a6', 'span_id': '019bfaac-7d28-77f3-9af1-c3fe0b27e74e', 'parent_span_id': '019bfaac-7d19-7f61-a1a5-801bbd45bb1e', 'component': 'llm', 'actor_type': 'agent', 'actor_id': 'worker', 'payload_json': '{"model": "/data/models/Qwen3-Omni-30B-A3B-Thinking-AWQ-4bit", "prompts_digest": "[\'Human: 你是 SQL 审核专家。审核以下 SQL 是否存在逻辑错误，并判断是否符合用户需求。\\\\n\\\\n**用户需求**：\\\\n查询orders_db数据库中各城市每月订单总金额，按城市和月份分组统计总金额，返回包含城市、月份、总金额三列的DataFrame结果\\\\n\\\\n**数据库 Schema**：\\\\n- agent_checkpoints: (id, thread_id, checkpoint_ns, checkpoint, version, created_at, updated_at)\\\\n- events: (id, ts, level, type, pipeline, node, stream_id, msg, extra)\\\\n- graphs: (id, name, requires, file_path, created_at, updated_at)\\\\n- logs: (id, ts, level, pipeline, node, stream_id, message, extra)\\\\n- m_cities: (id, name)\\\\n- m_customers: (id, name, city_id)\\\\n- m_orders: (id, customer_id, created_at, amount, status)\\\\n- models: (id, task, family, variant, path, conf, iou, created_at, updated_at)\\\\n- pipelines: (name, graph_id, default_model_id, encoder_cfg, created_at, updated_at)\\\\n- sessions: (id, stream_id, pipeline, model_id, status, error_msg, started_at, stopped_at)\\\\n- sources: (id, uri, status, caps, fps, created_at, updated_at)\\\\n- train_jobs: (id, status, phase, cfg, mlflow_run_id, registered_model, registered_version, metrics, artifacts, error)\\\\n\\\\n**待审核 SQL**：\\\\n```sql\\\\nSELECT \\\\n    mc.name AS city,\\\\n    DATE_FORMAT(mo.created_at, \\\\\'%Y-%m\\\\\') AS month,\\\\n    SUM(CAST(mo.amount AS DECIMAL(10, 2))) AS total_amount\\\\nFROM \\\\n    m_orders mo\\\\nJOIN \\\\n    m_customers mcust ON mo.customer_id = mcust.id\\\\nJOIN \\\\n    m_cities mc ON mcust.city_id = mc.id\\\\nWHERE \\\\n    mo.status = \\\\\'paid\\\\\'\\\\nGROUP BY \\\\n    city, month\\\\n```\\\\n\\\\n**审核清单**：\\\\n1. **JOIN 关联正确性**：JOIN 条件是否通过正确的外键关联？是否会产生笛卡尔积？\\\\n2. **语义正确性**（最重要）：\\\\n   - SELECT 的字段必须来自语义正确的表。根据 Schema 中的外键关系判断。\\\\n   - 如果用户要查某个维度的统计（如城市、类别），SELECT 的名称字段必须来自该维度的最终表，不能来自中间关联表。\\\\n   - SELECT 的别名应该反映其真实含义。\\\\n3. **聚合粒度**：\\\\n   - 如果用户需要\\"饼图/占比/分布\\"，SQL 应该只按一个维度聚合（如只 GROUP BY city_name）。\\\\n   - 如果用户需要\\"趋势图/时序图\\"，SQL 应该包含时间维度聚合。\\\\n4. **GROUP BY (宽松模式)**：只要 SELECT 中的非聚合列在 GROUP BY 中出现且逻辑正确，就通过。\\\\n\\\\n**回复格式**（必须是有效 JSON）：\\\\n{\\"approved\\": true, \\"issues\\": [], \\"suggestion\\": \\"\\"}\\\\n或\\\\n{\\"approved\\": false, \\"issues\\": [\\"问题描述\\"], \\"suggestion\\": \\"建议的修复方式\\"}\\\\n\\\\n只返回 JSON，不要其他内容。\']"}'}
