ies), month from created_at, and SUM(amount). But need to make sure that the month is correctly extracted.\\\\n\\\\nAlso, the tables: m_orders has customer_id, which joins to m_customers.id. Then m_customers.city_id joins to m_cities.id. So the joins are necessary.\\\\n\\\\nSo steps:\\\\n\\\\n1. Join m_orders to m_customers on customer_id = m_customers.id.\\\\n2. Join m_customers to m_cities on city_id = m_cities.id.\\\\n3. Extract the month from created_at. Let\\\\\'s say using EXTRACT(MONTH FROM created_at) as month.\\\\n4. Group by city name and month, sum amount.\\\\n\\\\nBut the problem says \\"每月订单总金额\\", so per month and city.\\\\n\\\\nWait, the created_at is a datetime string. Maybe in PostgreSQL, EXTRA", "name": "format_output", "langgraph_node": "format_output", "subagent": null}'}
